Second Department,

Mat, 1959 *

(May 18, 1959) The People of the State of New York, Respondent, v. Thomas Kling, Appellant.

Motion for reargument of motion to dispense with printing and for other relief denied. Present — Wenzel, Acting P. J., Beldock, Murphy, Hallinan and Kleinfeld, JJ.
